rm2=fff\n  |body2=fff\n  |rightarm2=fff\n  |shorts2=fff\n  |socks2=fff\n  | prevseason = 1986\u201387 \n  | nextseason = 1988\u201389\n}}\n\nIn the '''1987\u201388''' season [[Panathinaikos F.C.|Panathinaikos]] played in Greece's top division, the [[Superleague Greece|Alpha Ethniki]]. They also competed in the [[UEFA Cup]] and the [[1987\u201388 Greek Cup|Greek Cup]].\n\n==Squad==\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Antonis Minou]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Nikos Sarganis]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Kostas Mavridis]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Nikos Karoulias]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Lysandros Georgamlis]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Christos Vasileiou]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Nikos Vamvakoulas]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Kostas Antoniou]]|pos=MF}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=AUS|name=[[Chris Kalantzis]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Vangelis Vlachos]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=CRO|name=[[Velimir Zajec]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Dimitris Saravakos]]|pos=MF|other=[[Captain (association football)|captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=ARG|name=[[Juan Ramon Rocha]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Paris Georgakopoulos]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Thanasis Dimopoulos]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=|nat=GRE|name=[[Christos Dimopoulos]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n==Competitions==\n\n===Alpha Ethniki===\n====Classification====\n{{:1987\u201388 Alpha Ethniki|showteam=PAT}}\n\n===UEFA Cup===\n'''First round'''\n{{TwoLegStart}}\n{{TwoLegResult|'''[[Panathinaikos F.C.|Panathinaikos]]'''|Greece| 4\u20133 |[[AJ Auxerre]]|France|6= 2\u20130 ([http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=1987/matches/round=605/match=4252/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report])|7= 2\u20133 ([http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=1987/matches/round=605/match=4253/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report])}}\n|}\n'''Second round'''\n{{TwoLegS